+## AI Governance API
+
+- `POST /telemetry/ingest`
+- `GET /ai-governance/providers`
+- `GET /ai-governance/keys`
+- `GET /ai-governance/usage?days=7`
+- `GET /ai-governance/subscriptions`
+- `GET /ai-governance/alerts`
+- `POST /ai-governance/alerts/{id}/resolve`
+- `GET /shadow-ai/events`
+
 ## What This Proves
 
 - Policy enforcement works inline before tool execution (allow, block, require approval).
